modName: SkyVoice Words Renamed Dragonborn Optional Plugin
summary: Renames the words of power from Dragonborn. Meant for use with SkyVoice (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28448/ )
descriptionHtml:
I don\'t like when there\'s inconsistencies in my user interface >_<

In this case it was that the wonderful folks over at SkyVoice had made optional shout rename files for vanilla Skyrim and for Dawnguard, but not for Dragonborn. So I decided to fix that! My very first mod, took me all of about four minutes.

SkyVoice is available here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28448/
Awesome mod. Check it out.


This does *NOT* require SkyVoice but truthfully I can\'t imagine why you\'d want it if you aren\'t already using their mod and their other optional plugins.
author: CommanderNeph
